snippet.textDisplay:
The music producer deserves exceptional recognition !! The way he treats the folk vocals is refreshing. The groove, so danceable, yet with such a soft poise, the Bansi melodies, the choir, and to my surprise Neha Kakkar's vocals blend in so well. Kudos to Dig V, who highlighted her lower register, rather in the melodies, and the upper register in the more nasal tone, as a counter melody, almost a piccolo. 

In this song, nothing stands out. And that is beautiful, because everything blends in so well, again the dolby atmosphere helps here. 

Exquisite set design as well. Well, coke studio Bharat, you have produced a song that will be appreciated the ages long.
